    {
        "content": "<p>If someone put a gun to my head I would try to prove that fin (succ d) -&gt; Z was the product of fin d -&gt; Z and Z, show that the corresponding filter was an \"or\", prove that filtering on P or Q gave me at most as many elements as summing the sizes of filtering on P and on Q etc etc etc.</p>",
